external_knowledge:
- "blossoming categories" refers to categories with high total hits and volunteer requests;
- "attracting the most views" refers to having a high total hits value;
- "attracting the most volunteer requests" refers to having a high total vol_requests value;
- "rank in these two aspects of popularity" refers to the ranks based on total hits and total volunteer requests.

sql:
SELECT title, vol_requests
FROM opportunities
ORDER BY vol_requests DESC;
